Definition: an acting technique introduced by Stanislavsky in which the actor recalls emotions or reactions from his or her own life and uses them to identify with the character being portrayed
Synonyms: method, acting, an, technique, introduced, by, Stanislavsky, in, which, the, actor, recalls, emotions, or, reactions, from, his, her, own, life, and, uses, them, to, identify, with, character, being, portrayed
Category: noun.act
